### Basic scenario
## Very simple alarm: Pushing a button activates a LED and a buzzer. Releasing the button switches the actuators off.

application simpleAlarm

# Declaring bricks
sensor buttonOne: 8
sensor buttonTwo: 9
actuator buzzer: 11

# Declaring states
on {
    buzzer <= HIGH
    buttonOne is LOW op OR with buttonTwo is LOW => off
}

-> off {
    buzzer <= LOW
    buttonOne is HIGH op AND with buttonTwo is HIGH => on
}